{"data":[{"date":"09:25 02/07","title":"Su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 Luka Modric n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/messi-chang-phai-la-dang-cuu-the-trong-su-cuong-si-cua-nguoi-ham-mo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 1 qu\u1ea3 11m nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i vui m\u1eebng khi Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m \u1edf hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCroatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 3-2 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Luka Modric v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho 8 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Luka-Modric-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Dan-Mach-vs-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Modric b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf ph\u00fat 114</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Croatia. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ph\u00fat 114, Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m sau khi Mathias Jorgensen ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Ante Rebic trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m 11m v\u00e0 Luka Modric b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, tuy nhi\u00ean anh l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kasper Schmeichel khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 penalty c\u00e2n n\u00e3o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea5t may cho Modric l\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ha-dan-mach-vao-tu-ket-hlv-croatia-noi-gi-421-190147.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Croatia kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1ch Modric </span>sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng anh \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Luka Modric th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau khi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 1 qu\u1ea3 11m nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i vui m\u1eebng khi Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric noi ve tran Dan Mach vs Croatia\" title=\"Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/messi-chang-phai-la-dang-cuu-the-trong-su-cuong-si-cua-nguoi-ham-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Nga, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng Croatia c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"811","checkdouble":"190151"},{"date":"09:16 02/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7): Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-nhat-ban-1h00-ngay-37-lieu-co-them-dia-chan.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng n\u00e0o cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng cao. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p khi h\u01a1n Senegal v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 fair-play m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FIFA \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, B\u1ec9 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 37) Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 37) Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Nhan-dinh-Bi-vs-Nhat-Ban-(1h00-ngay-37)-Lieu-co-them-dia-chan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Hazard, De Bruyne kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t khi ghi 9 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 sau 3 tr\u1eadn. S\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Hazard, Lukaku, Mertens, De Bruyne. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 &quot;th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng&quot;. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Roberto Martinez c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Lukaku \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n. \u0110T Nh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf nh\u1eefng pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn khi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao trung b\u00ecnh th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-dt-anh-that-bai-truoc-bi-466-189957.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/3-ly-do-khien-dt-anh-that-bai-truoc-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-dt-anh-that-bai-truoc-bi-466-189957.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t duy nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00eam qua. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong khi Anh \u0111\u1ee5ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Colombia nh\u1edd chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00f4 duy\u00ean ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Carlos Sanchez, h\u00f2a Senegal khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01a1i l\u1ecfng \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Tr\u1eadn thua Ba Lan cho th\u1ea5y Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u01a1i k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u toan t\u00ednh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i World Cup v\u1eabn l\u00e0 v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u01a1i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c &quot;samurai xanh&quot; kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng l\u1edbn ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Akira Nishino c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec5n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Bi vs Nhat Ban\" title=\"Preview B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Bi-vs-Nhat.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: \u00d4ng l\u1edbn ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a?</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga c\u0169ng v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00e1c khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tham kh\u1ea3o b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, ch\u01a1i l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 do \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1ng n\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0110T B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung \u0111\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup \u1edf 6/7 l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hai l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 1986 v\u00e0 2014.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi trong c\u1ea3 11 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup, thua 8 (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1). Trong s\u1ed1 9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0110T B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i k\u00e9o d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 trong 5 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 (9). H\u1ecd c\u0169ng to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Croatia v\u00e0 Uruguay.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* B\u1ec9 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 22 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng 17, h\u00f2a 5).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 2, thua 3).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 World Cup n\u0103m 1998, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ee9 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1i gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (2002, 2010, 2018) nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111i xa h\u01a1n v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ec9 (3-4-2-1): </strong>1.Courtois - 2.Alderweireld, 20.Boyata, 5.Vertonghen - 15.Meunier, 7.De Bruyne, 6.Witsel, 11.Carrasco - 14.Mertens, 10.Hazard - 9.Lukaku</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Kawashima - 19.Sakai, 3.Shoji, 22.Yoshida, 5.Nagatomo - 17.Hasebe, 7.Shibasaki - 8.Haraguchi, 10.Kagawa, 14.Inui - 15.Osako</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:</strong> B\u1ec9 3-1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Bi vs Nhat Ban\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Bi-vs-Nhat-Ban-(3-4-2-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bi-nhm-dang-co-danh-gia-sai-lam-ve-de-bruyne-421-190001.html\">HLV B\u1ec9: NHM \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 sai l\u1ea7m v\u1ec1 De Bruyne</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/alexis-sanchez-dua-ra-du-doan-doi-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-189982.html\">Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u01b0a ra d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-bi-nhan-3-tin-mung-truoc-tran-gap-nhat-ban-421-189979.html\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn 3 tin m\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-dt-anh-that-bai-truoc-bi-466-189957.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vuot-qua-vong-bang-mot-cach-kho-tin-hlv-nhat-ban-noi-gi-421-189893.html\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 tin, HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/keisuke-honda-nguoi-giup-nhat-ban-nuoi-duong-hy-vong-di-tiep-421-189870.html\">Keisuke Honda: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"810","checkdouble":"190153"},{"date":"09:34 02/07","title":"Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201ckh\u1eafc tinh\u201d c\u1ee7a Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/15/barca-muon-mua-kante-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kasper Schmeichel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia, d\u00f9 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kasper Schmeichel ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Croatia v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n mi\u1ebfng tr\u1ea3 mi\u1ebfng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kasper Schmeichel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kasper Schmeichel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Kasper-Schmeichel-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Dan-Mach-vs-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kasper Schmeichel ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, anh c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester c\u00f2n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m c\u1ee7a Modric \u1edf ph\u00fat 114.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Kasper Schmeichel c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Thua 2-3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty c\u00e2n n\u00e3o, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-dan-mach-421-190118.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kasper Schmeichel c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o d\u00f9 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kasper Schmeichel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia, d\u00f9 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Schmeichel noi ve tran Dan Mach vs Croatia\" title=\"Schmeichel n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/dan-mach-bi-loai-thu-mon-schmeichel-van-cam-thay-tu-hao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Schmeichel n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c NHM c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0o t\u1eeb ng\u1eef v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3 11m c\u1ee7a Modric, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111i ti\u1ebfp\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"809","checkdouble":"190155"},{"date":"09:55 02/07","title":"\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/marlon-chuan-bi-gia-nhap-southampton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Barcelona c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn CLB c\u1ee7a Premier League v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Marlon kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarlon t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Marlon Santos da Silva Barbosa, sinh ng\u00e0y 7 th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m 1995. Anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barcelona t\u1eeb Fluminense d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2016/17. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Blaugrana k\u00fd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng do kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi Ernesto Valverde, Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em Marlon cho Nice c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Fluminense m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton t\u1eeb Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton t\u1eeb Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/marlon-chuan-bi-gia-nhap-southampton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton t\u1eeb Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNice kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Marlon v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 anh l\u1ea1i Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 Valverde v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Southampton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Marlon c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Barca. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Premier League n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00e0 Southampton v\u00e0 West Ham \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Blaugrana.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n Nam n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i. Trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Marlon s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Southampton ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a CLB n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Marlon s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Southampton h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Stuart Armstrong t\u1eeb Celtic v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Basler Mohamed Elyounoussi t\u1eeb Basel. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, The Saints \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn Andrea Petagna c\u1ee7a Atalanta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-barca-172-189954.html\">Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/rafinha-muon-roi-barca-cang-som-cang-tot-180-189772.html\">Sao Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Neymar sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia-180-189646.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pogba Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-va-real-dai-chien-vi-sao-bayern-munich-180-189512.html\">Barca v\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"808","checkdouble":"190156"},{"date":"09:51 02/07","title":"M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \"Pogba Serbia\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Lazio.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus quan t\u00e2m Sergej Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Juventus-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-dang-rat-kho-khan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lazio, anh ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, anh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Serie A c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/doi-bong-cua-serie-a-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-sao-khung-arsenal-172-189741.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lazio quan t\u00e2m Ramsey</span> c\u1ee7a Arsenal cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Lazio.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Lazio-muon-mua-Aaron-Ramsey-thay-Milinkovic-Savic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Lazio d\u00e0nh cho Milinkovic-Savic khi\u1ebfn Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, theo Tuttosport, Lazio \u0111\u00f2i 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rodrigo Bentancur m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, n\u1ebfu Juventus kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u00e0 Juventus g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat lui trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 80 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n MU, PSG v\u00e0 Barca l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Lazio y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Milinkovic-Savic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"807","checkdouble":"190157"},{"date":"10:44 02/07","title":"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Schmeichel v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/dan-mach-bi-loai-thu-mon-schmeichel-van-cam-thay-tu-hao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kasper Schmeichel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia, d\u00f9 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kasper Schmeichel ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Croatia v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n mi\u1ebfng tr\u1ea3 mi\u1ebfng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kasper Schmeichel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kasper Schmeichel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Kasper-Schmeichel-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Dan-Mach-vs-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kasper Schmeichel ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, anh c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester c\u00f2n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m c\u1ee7a Modric \u1edf ph\u00fat 114.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Kasper Schmeichel c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Thua 2-3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty c\u00e2n n\u00e3o, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-dan-mach-421-190118.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kasper Schmeichel c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o d\u00f9 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kasper Schmeichel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia, d\u00f9 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Schmeichel noi ve tran Dan Mach vs Croatia\" title=\"Schmeichel n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/dan-mach-bi-loai-thu-mon-schmeichel-van-cam-thay-tu-hao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Schmeichel n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c NHM c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0o t\u1eeb ng\u1eef v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3 11m c\u1ee7a Modric, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111i ti\u1ebfp\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"806","checkdouble":"190158"},{"date":"11:00 02/07","title":"HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/hlv-nhat-ban-muon-lam-nen-dia-chan-truoc-dt-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng HLV Akira Nishino v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n khi \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p nh\u1edd hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 &quot;fair-play&quot; m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FIFA \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i khi g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. D\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng &quot;samurai xanh&quot; v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nhat Ban muon lam nen dia chan truoc cuoc doi dau voi DT Bi\" title=\"HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/hlv-nhat-ban-muon-lam-nen-dia-chan-truoc-dt-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Akira Nishino cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y hai l\u1ea7n trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c n\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u1edbi. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 to l\u1edbn trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn n\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u1ece v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, ch\u00ednh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Colombia, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n khi h\u1ea1 \u0110\u1ee9c. \u1ede v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi lo\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 s\u1edf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i World Cup v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2002 v\u00e0 2010. &quot;Samurai xanh&quot; c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng HLV Akira Nishino ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-nhat-ban-1h00-ngay-37-lieu-co-them-dia-chan-462-190153.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-nhat-ban-1h00-ngay-37-lieu-co-them-dia-chan.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-nhat-ban-1h00-ngay-37-lieu-co-them-dia-chan-462-190153.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7): Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n?</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</br>HLV Nishino ch\u1ec9 ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t: &quot;\u1ede nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 ba c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u toan t\u00ednh trong c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thua B\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tinh th\u1ea7n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn, B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 gh\u00ea g\u1edbm, h\u1ecd n\u1eb1m trong top 3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 th\u1eadt k\u1ef9 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, khi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed 61&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.\r\n<h2><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-bi-nhan-3-tin-mung-truoc-tran-gap-nhat-ban-421-189979.html\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn 3 tin m\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/xep-bet-bang-h-hlv-ba-lan-noi-gi-421-189904.html\">X\u1ebfp b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng H, HLV Ba Lan n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vuot-qua-vong-bang-mot-cach-kho-tin-hlv-nhat-ban-noi-gi-421-189893.html\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 tin, HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-sau-tran-nhat-ban-01-colombia-421-189891.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 0-1 Ba Lan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/keisuke-honda-nguoi-giup-nhat-ban-nuoi-duong-hy-vong-di-tiep-421-189870.html\">Keisuke Honda: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-nhan-dinh-dt-nhat-ban-an-may-kho-di-sau-168-189526.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0103n may, kh\u00f3 \u0111i s\u00e2u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"805","checkdouble":"190159"},{"date":"10:55 02/07","title":"Ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i khuy\u00ean Gareth Bale b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/gareth-bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-real-ve-voi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng vinh quang m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh M.U v\u00e0 \u0110T x\u1ee9 Wales, Mickey Thomas.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bale mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid, Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 1 La Liga v\u00e0 4 Champions League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales mong mu\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1eady. Ngay sau khi c\u00f9ng Real \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Champions League m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 th\u00e1ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBale mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1i Real. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 6 th\u00f4i, Jonathan Barnett - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Bale c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tottenham n\u00f3i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Gareth-Bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-Real-ve-voi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bale c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Real Madrid h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Real</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi \u201cC\u01a1n l\u1ed1c x\u1ee9 Wales\u201d bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Bayern Munich c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0 Premier League. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 M.U v\u00e0 x\u1ee9 Wales: Mickey Thomas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGareth Bale kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau\u201d, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 63 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. \u201cCV c\u1ee7a Bale \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. T\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Bale \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. N\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale\" title=\"Bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/gareth-bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-real-ve-voi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u1ea1i Premier League</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan United, Chelsea r\u1ed3i Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi Gareth Bale. V\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i Thomas tin \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi l\u00fac h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i Premier League. \u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may, Bale \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Neymar ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u, Bale s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i cho Bayern Munich, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi l\u00fac ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh \u1edf Premier League.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ryan-giggs-khuyen-mourinho-ky-hop-dong-voi-sao-real-madrid-172-189040.html\">Ryan Giggs khuy\u00ean Mourinho k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi sao Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-united-chuan-bi-dua-gareth-bale-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-172-188500.html\">Man United chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0a Gareth Bale l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u201ckh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-tuong-lai-ronaldo-va-bale-nuong-nhau-ma-song-180-188128.html\">Chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo v\u00e0 Bale: N\u01b0\u01a1ng nhau m\u00e0 s\u1ed1ng!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/bo-vo-tuong-lai-bi-cam-tham-du-dam-cuoi-cua-bale-188-187786.html\">B\u1ed1 v\u1ee3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Bale</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-moi-goi-gareth-bale-den-old-trafford-172-187570.html\">C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Gareth Bale \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"804","checkdouble":"190161"},{"date":"10:58 02/07","title":"Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/real-madrid-da-co-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 BL\u0110 Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Modric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Toni Kroos h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Tuong-lai-Luka-Modric-da-duoc-quyet-dinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn cho Real Madrid, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 theo \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Don Balon, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/bayern-munich-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-sao-real-madrid-180-189278.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Luka Modric</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tottenham v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edd Mirror c\u1ee7a Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 40 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 BL\u0110 Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Modric\" title=\"tien ve Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/real-madrid-da-co-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n40 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng si\u00eau l\u00f2ng, nh\u01b0ng Real Madrid th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Modric v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sergio Ramos c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Real Madrid b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, anh tin r\u1eb1ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Modric v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Modric \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf Nga. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"803","checkdouble":"190162"},{"date":"10:59 02/07","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 2/7: Sergio Ramos \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/ngay-hom-nay-27.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (2/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>Sergio Ramos \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 sau lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.\u00a0 Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a La Roja. Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00ec \u0111i \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o HLV c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 Fernando Hierro. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c su\u1ed1t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/180702_035015_132.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a La Roja Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i suy ngh\u0129 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u1ea9ng cao. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 11m ngay t\u1eeb khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i World Cup cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i theo c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u201cL\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn hi\u1ebfn v\u00ec chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Nga \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Igor Akinfeev cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p may trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. \u1ede hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 mong ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11 m. Th\u1eadt may khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa\u201d.</div>\r\n<h2>Iniesta t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andres Iniesta ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 v\u1edbi La Roja. \"\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha. K\u1ebft th\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt\".\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-chia-tay-huyen-thoai-trong-tang-toc-421-190132.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/tay-ban-nha-chia-tay-huyen-thoai-trong-tang-toc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-chia-tay-huyen-thoai-trong-tang-toc-421-190132.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha chia tay huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i trong tang t\u00f3c</span><br>\r\n<span>Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Putin ch\u00fac m\u1eebng tuy\u1ec3n Nga</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo t\u1edd TASS, t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Nga Putin d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng v\u1eabn theo d\u00f5i qua truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c g\u1eedi l\u1eddi ch\u00fac m\u1eebng t\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \"T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi d\u1ef1 do b\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u1eabn theo d\u00f5i qua truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho HLV Cherchesov ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng\". Th\u01b0 k\u00fd ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng, Peskov ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<h2>Marcelo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo NBC Sport \u0111\u01b0a tin, HLV Tite x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. Marcelo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay anh l\u00e0 Filipe Luis.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-21h-ngay-27-cho-doi-tran-cau-kinh-dien-421-190148.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-21h-ngay-27-cho-doi-tran-cau-kinh-dien.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-21h-ngay-27-cho-doi-tran-cau-kinh-dien-421-190148.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico (21h ng\u00e0y 2/7): Ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n</span><br>\r\n<span>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i m\u1edbi bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Kane ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u0103ng hoa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u1eeba ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u0103ng hoa t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 nh\u1edd b\u1ecf qua m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i. \"T\u00f4i r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eeb EURO 2016. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecdc qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u Twitter v\u00e0 ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn thi\u1ebfu t\u1eadp trung trong thi \u0111\u1ea5u. N\u0103m nay, t\u00f4i n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ghi b\u00e0n\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"802","checkdouble":"190163"},{"date":"07:01 02/07","title":"De Gea nh\u1eadn \"m\u01b0a g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1\" sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f3 tin \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/de-gea-bi-nhan-mua-gach-da-sau-man-trinh-dien-kho-tin-o-world-cup-2018.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1eebng c\u1ee9u thua 18 l\u1ea7n trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League nh\u01b0ng khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup, David De Gea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 2 pha c\u1ee9u thua trong 4 tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. </h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn m\u01b0a g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1 sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn m\u01b0a g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1 sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/0.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">K\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi David De Gea. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Man Utd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m s\u01a1 \u0111\u1eb3ng m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd ph</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea nh\u1eadn m\u01b0a g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1 sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f3 tin \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"De Gea nh\u1eadn m\u01b0a g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1 sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f3 tin \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/De-Gea-nhan-mua-gach-da-sau-man-trinh-dien-kho-tin-o-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a&nbsp; \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 6 l\u1ea7n. M\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Akinfeev thuc hien 2 pha cuu thua chi tinh rieng trong loat sut luan luu voi Tay Ban Nha. Trong khi do, De Gea chi co 1 lan can pha thanh cong trong 4 tran dau tai World Cup 2018\" title=\"Akinfeev th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 2 pha c\u1ee9u thua ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh ri\u00eang trong lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, De Gea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/065558-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Trang Twitter ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a FIFA: Akinfeev th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 2 pha c\u1ee9u thua ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh ri\u00eang trong lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, De Gea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Co le Luis Suarez lam thu mon cho Tay Ban Nha se tot hon la De Gea, CDV OMAR lay pha choi bong bang tay cua Suarez tai World Cup 2010 de che nhao thu mon cua Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"C\u00f3 l\u1ebd Luis Suarez l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 De Gea, C\u0110V OMAR l\u1ea5y pha ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng tay c\u1ee7a Suarez t\u1ea1i World Cup 2010 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/4.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&quot;C\u00f3 l\u1ebd Luis Suarez l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 De Gea&quot;, C\u0110V c\u00f3 t\u00ean OMAR l\u1ea5y pha ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng tay c\u1ee7a Suarez t\u1ea1i World Cup 2010 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"World Cup nam nay giup chung ta hieu ra rang: De Gea co choi hay den dau cung khong bao gio du kha nang thay the huyen thoai Iker Casillas\" title=\"World Cup n\u0103m nay gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta hi\u1ec3u ra r\u1eb1ng: De Gea c\u00f3 ch\u01a1i hay \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Iker Casillas\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/3_1.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">World Cup n\u0103m nay gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta hi\u1ec3u ra r\u1eb1ng: De Gea c\u00f3 ch\u01a1i hay \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Iker Casillas</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea qua te hai. Toi se phai tiep tuc chung kien anh ta dung trong khung go cua Man Utd hang tuan 10 nam toi\" title=\"De Gea qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1