\u00fat th\u1ee9 10, d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf ch\u0103m s\u00f3c nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico, HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Marcelo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico, HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Marcelo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Truoc-tran-gap-Mexico,-HLV-Tite-phat-bieu-ve-Marcelo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcelo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Serbia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Brazil x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/tiet-lo-cuc-soc-ve-chan-thuong-cua-marcelo-421-189879.html\" target=\"_blank\">Marcelo b\u1ecb co th\u1eaft c\u01a1 l\u01b0ng</span>, b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 Rodrigo Lasmar c\u1ee7a Selecao kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 do t\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ec7m tr\u00ean gi\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ee7 trong kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00eda Brazil c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 Marcelo g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tin r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 samba b\u1edfi ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real quan tr\u1ecdng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1edbi Selecao th\u00ec ai c\u0169ng r\u00f5.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNHM \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5y Marcelo c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Marcelo ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Marcelo, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcelo se ngoi du bi o tran dau voi Mexico\" title=\"Marcelo s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/da-co-ket-luan-ve-kha-nang-da-chinh-cua-marcelo-truoc-mexico.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcelo s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tham gia bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt, Marcelo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111au nh\u1eb9. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, Felipe Luis s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay Marcelo&rdquo;.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Brazil, song t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Mexico l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Brazil s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"799","checkdouble":"190145"},{"date":"08:36 02/07","title":"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh: Croatia v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i sau lo\u1ea1t penalty c\u00e2n n\u00e3o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/hinh-anh-croatia-va-dan-mach-phan-thang-bai-sau-loat-penalty-can-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Modric v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nCroatia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edbm nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua t\u1eeb ngay ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, khi Mathias Jorgensen c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u1ed9n x\u1ed9n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m. Nh\u01b0ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u01b0a Croatia tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 cho \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 116 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 2, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, Luka Modric kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kasper Schmeichel, khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang may r\u1ee7i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Schmeichel v\u00e0 Subasic li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ee9u thua ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 - khi c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00e1 k\u00e9m. Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/083151-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a C\u0110V Croatia tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Jorgensen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/083142-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jorgensen m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Mandzukic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/083132-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u01b0ng Mandzukic c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Rebic ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 11m cho Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/083120-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h