         <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 7\" title=\"Kasper Schmeichel\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/083019-7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kasper Schmeichel th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 8\" title=\"Rakitic s\u00fat th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/hinh-anh-croatia-va-dan-mach-phan-thang-bai-sau-loat-penalty-can-nao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rakitic s\u00fat th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 9\" title=\"Croatia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/083000-8.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Croatia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00e1 k\u00e9m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 10\" title=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/082947-10.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc trong ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-dan-mach-461-190123.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/575d89ee-36bf-44f3-b721-1b08ef-5349-9855-1530469531_600x0.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-dan-mach-461-190123.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 1-1 (pen 3-2) \u0110an M\u1ea1ch (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nMa\u0300n tri\u0300nh di\u00ea\u0303n xu\u00e2\u0301t s\u0103\u0301c cu\u0309a thu\u0309 tha\u0300nh Subasic tr\u00ean ch\u00e2\u0301m 11m, khi ca\u0309n pha\u0301 tha\u0300nh c\u00f4ng 3 cu\u0301i d\u01b0\u0301t \u0111i\u00ea\u0309m cu\u0309a c\u00e2\u0300u thu\u0309 \u0110an Ma\u0323ch \u0111a\u0303 giu\u0301p \u0110T Croatia...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/luka-modric-ngon-co-dau-cua-nguoi-croatia-389-190104.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/luka-modric-ngon-co-dau-cua-nguoi-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/luka-modric-ngon-co-dau-cua-nguoi-croatia-389-190104.html\">Luka Modric: Ng\u1ecdn c\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia</span><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Modric ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1eadp trung cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 World Cup quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0m t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"798","checkdouble":"190146"},{"date":"08:54 02/07","title":"H\u1ea1 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, HLV Croatia n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/ha-dan-mach-vao-tu-ket-hlv-croatia-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia h\u1ea1 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCroatia v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n t\u00e0i c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. \u1ede gi\u00e2y th\u1ee9 58 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Jorgensen, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 sau \u0111\u00f3 3 ph\u00fat Mario Mandzukic g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Croatia di tiep\" title=\"Croatia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/083000-8.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Croatia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng b\u00ean n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o hai hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5. Ph\u00fat 114, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJorgensen c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 1 qu\u1ea3 11m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kasper Schmeichel.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec th\u1ebf ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng lo\u1ea1t penalty. Tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00e2n n\u00e3o Croatia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-dan-mach-421-190118.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Zlatko Dalic h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zlatko Dalic phat bieu ve tran Dan Mach vs Croatia\" title=\"Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/ha-dan-mach-vao-tu-ket-hlv-croatia-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Danijel Subasic l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Croatia t\u1ed1i nay, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty c\u00e2n n\u00e3o, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd phong \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Hy v\u1ecdng Subasic s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"797","checkdouble":"190147"}]}